THE LORAX IS COMING

A demo of what is to come

BY SUNNY

Data
====
Windows: run demo-WINDOWS
Linux: run demo-LINUX
version 0.0.0-demo-1

Controls
========
Space: use tool
Arrows: move around
Best experienced with headphones at a high volume to hear the subtleties of the ambient soundscape.

Goals of playing
================
1) Come up with ideas
2) Try to crash the program mercilessly (post crashes on the discord)
3) See how bad I am at art and that I have a twisted sense of humor
4) Enjoy!

yes i know the pickaxe is from minecraft
